item.title: CAO Assignment
item.description: In our assignment we were asked to make a 64 bit Operating system. We followed the guidlines given in the two videos provided to us. Multiboot 2 Bootloader According to the video, we will make a x_86 compatible operating system with multiboot 2 bootloader. The multiboot 2 has certain files stored on it that are loaded in to memory when the bootloader boots the kernel. Qemu Qemu is an opensource emulator that does hardware virtualization.
